Carma,is,a,rideshare,carpooling,app,that,allows,users,to,find,local,passengers,with,similar,destinations,in,order,to,share,a,commute,and,reduce,cost,and,traffic,emissions,giving,drivers,a,little,bit,of,cash,along,the,way,The,Carma,API,can,be,used,by,developers,to,create,apps,and,features,based,on,Carma,traffic,data,and,driving,behaviors,WIth,the,API,developers,can,integrate,extensive,carpooling,functionality,such,as,search,matching,trip,recording,booking,and,messaging,Possible,use,cases,include,an,app,that,logs,Carma,data,to,motivate,carpooling,integration,with,a,mapping,app,that,automatically,shows,multiple,transportation,options,carpool,matching,within,an,events,application,and,more,The,international,Carama,service,is,operational,in,Austin,Bergen,Cork,San,Francisco,Dublin,San,Diego,Los,Angeles,and,other,US,cities